## Delete this section from your issue.
Fill out this for making suggestions/requests, failure to do so will result in your issue being closed without being read.

#### Feature being requested

Include a brief description of what you want added here.  it should be as concise as possible.

#### Details on feature/suggestion

Include a more expanded description of the feature here.  Please include all details you can about it, including how the feature should act ingame, what things should look like, and how players should interact with it.
